{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/googleapis/release-please/main/schemas/config.json",
  "//": [
    "Two independent packages, like DrummyFloyd/crunchy-userinit-controller:",
    "  - \".\": the platform app — bumps images, the vX.Y.Z git tag ArgoCD",
    "    tracks (Application targetRevision), and Chart.yaml's appVersion",
    "    (default image tag). ArgoCD deploys straight from git, so this tag",
    "    is the actual deployable-state contract.",
    "  - \"helm/waas\": the chart's OWN SemVer (Chart.yaml `version`), bumped",
    "    only by changes under helm/, used solely for the OCI chart artifact",
    "    pushed for external `helm install --version` consumers. It can",
    "    legitimately diverge from the app version between chart releases —",
    "    that's normal Helm practice, not a bug.",
    "appVersion keeps its 'v' prefix because the generic updater only",
    "rewrites the numeric part inside the x-release-please block."
  ],
  "bump-minor-pre-major": true,
  "separate-pull-requests": true,
  "sequential-calls": true,
  "always-update": true,
  "packages": {
    ".": {
      "package-name": "waas",
      "release-type": "simple",
      "changelog-path": "CHANGELOG.md",
      "exclude-paths": ["helm/waas/"],
      "extra-files": ["helm/waas/Chart.yaml"]
    },
    "helm/waas": {
      "package-name": "waas-chart",
      "release-type": "helm",
      "include-v-in-tag": false,
      "changelog-path": "CHANGELOG.md",
      "changelog-sections": [
        { "type": "feat", "section": "Features" },
        { "type": "fix", "section": "Bug Fixes" },
        { "type": "chore", "section": "Chores" }
      ]
    }
  }
}
